description: El Toro The Tot is an amazing gourmet food truck serving delicious Spanish-American burgers and tasty tater tots to the hungry people in the Denver area. From the Spanish Blue to the Veggie, these burgers are rich, juicy, and will have you coming back for more every day. And don't miss the stuffed tots, filled with cheese, and even bacon if you ask!
name: El Toro The Tot
